title: ONE MORE TIME
body_text:
Perhaps the year's finest clash
one more time
in this epic DODGEBALL CXL return contest. Blocking magician
Justin Wolf
looks to punt number one adversary
Juan Londono
out of DODGEBALL 150 contention. If the
140th spectacular
is any indication, this anxiously-awaited rematch will set new standards.
Those who love this game cannot miss out on this soon-to-be-classic. Catch DODGEBALL 142 June 14 only at Wall High School!
